@dev Implements the BNB-Bank
 Allows user to deposit and withdraw funds

@dev Deposit funds in the bank.
 A check for adequate user funds in MetaMask will be conducted client side.

@dev Withdraw funds from the bank and receive DBC Token interest.
 Interest is hard coded to 1 DBC Token

constructor.details: Create the Bank contract, assumes a Token contract has been deployed already. Requires manually changing the minter of the Token to the owner of the Bank contract. *An alternative would be to instantiate the Token here, so the the bank is minter

withdrawWithInterest().details: Withdraw funds from the bank and receive DBC Token interest. Interest is hard coded to 1 DBC Token
